data.description: SELLER'S ARE MOTIVATED!! MAKE AN OFFER!! LOCATION!! LOCATION!! LOCATION!! Landmark Pointe Community in Cibolo is the ideal family place to call home. Situated in close proximity to get to JBSA -Randolph, Brooks Air Force Base & JBSA- Ft Sam Houston, this home is centrally located to both Austin and San Antonio- 40 mins to Austin, 35 mins to San Antonio, 20 mins to SAT. As you enter the grand foyer, there are 2 bedrooms and hall bathroom.The first bedroom is great for In-Laws or older parents who need to be on the first floor only. The Master Bedroom w/ensuite is on the main floor, is large in size with a big walk-in closet. The Master bathroom has spa tub/shower combo, 2-sink vanity, so need to share with your spouse. Major Kitchen appliances, water softener & filtration system is included. Large Open floor plan, spacious kitchen with a granite island is perfect for entertaining on those Holiday events. Upstairs flex space is connected to the 4th bedroom with its own full bathroom, or work out room.
